member.name: T:AutoStep.Compiler.AutoStepCompiler
member.summary: Compiles individual AutoStep files and outputs built files.
member.remarks:
The AutoStep Compiler goes through the given file and parses it, outputting an in-memory definition of the file, including features, scenarios, steps etc.
The AutoStepLinker will go through the built output and bind it against a given project's available steps.
